WEBVTT

00:00:16.579 --> 00:00:27.631 line:90% position:50% align:center
Little one, so new to life,
In my arms I’ll hold you tight.

00:00:27.631 --> 00:00:36.640 line:90% position:50% align:center
You have nothing to fear;
I will always be near,

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:40.227 line:90% position:50% align:center
My little one.

00:00:44.064 --> 00:00:55.284 line:90% position:50% align:center
Little one, you’ll learn each day
To live life Jehovah’s way.

00:00:55.284 --> 00:01:04.251 line:90% position:50% align:center
You’re a gift from above;
you will always be loved,

00:01:04.251 --> 00:01:07.838 line:90% position:50% align:center
My little one.

00:01:11.592 --> 00:01:22.353 line:90% position:50% align:center
Soon you will see Paradise,
Yes, the life that Jehovah wants for you.

00:01:22.353 --> 00:01:30.527 line:90% position:50% align:center
With lions and bears you will play.
Yes, one day you will see all the things

00:01:30.527 --> 00:01:34.782 line:90% position:50% align:center
That God’s Kingdom brings.

00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:47.920 line:90% position:50% align:center
Little one, we’ll wait till then
And keep Jehovah our best Friend.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:56.679 line:90% position:50% align:center
You have nothing to fear;
he will always be near,

00:01:56.679 --> 00:02:06.230 line:90% position:50% align:center
My little one,
My little one,

00:02:07.982 --> 00:02:12.611 line:90% position:50% align:center
My little one.

